window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The time loop is coming to an end.</b></p> <p>With limited restarts remaining, Zorian and his allies must redouble their efforts to discover how they can prevent the release of an ancient primordial being once the time loop expires and they are returned to the real world—where choices can’t be undone.</p> <p><b>The thrilling next installment to the fan-loved Mother of Learning series by nobody103, writing as Domagoj Kurmaic!</b></p>"; 
